'''仙后座PZ'''（{{lang en|'''PZ Cassiopeiae'''}}），是一顆位於[[仙后座|仙后座]]的紅色[[超巨星|超巨星]]。這顆恆星是[[巨大恆星列表|至今人類已知體積最大的恆星]]之一，其半徑約為[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]的1,190–1,940倍。<ref name=levesqueetal2005>Table 4 in {{cite journal |title=The Effective Temperature Scale of Galactic Red Supergiants: Cool, but Not As Cool As We Thought |author=Emily M. Levesque, Philip Massey, K. A. G. Olsen, Bertrand Plez, Eric Josselin, Andre Maeder, and Georges Meynet |journal=The Astrophysical Journal |volume=628 |issue=2 |date=August 2005 |pages=973–985 |doi=10.1086/430901 |bibcode=2005ApJ...628..973L|arxiv = astro-ph/0504337 }}</ref>這顆恆星亦是紅超巨星中最明亮的恆星之一。這顆恆星距離地球約17800[[光年|光年]]。<ref name="Cornell"/>

==恆星狀況==
仙后座PZ是一顆紅[[超巨星|超巨星]]，其[[恆星光譜|恆星光譜]]分類為M3Iab，位於[[赫羅圖|赫羅圖]]的右上方。這代表這顆恆星的亮度極高，但[[有效溫度|有效溫度]]卻相對較低。<ref name="ResearchGate"/>天文學家估算這顆恆星的半徑為太陽半徑的1,190–1,940倍。雖然這顆恆星的體積比太陽大十億倍，但其質量僅僅約為[[太陽質量|太陽質量]]的數十倍。<ref name="Simbad"/>這顆恆星不單是其中一個體積最大的恆星，亦是紅超巨星中最明亮的恆星之一。其亮度約為太陽的數十萬倍，是其中一個最明亮的恆星。<ref name=Levesque>{{cite journal|last=Levesque|first=Emily M.|coauthors=Massey, Philip; Olsen, K. A. G.; Plez, Bertrand; Josselin, Eric; Maeder, Andre; Meynet, Georges|title=The Effective Temperature Scale of Galactic Red Supergiants: Cool, but Not as Cool as We Thought|journal=The Astrophysical Journal|date=1 August 2005|volume=628|issue=2|pages=973–985|doi=10.1086/430901|arxiv = astro-ph/0504337 |bibcode = 2005ApJ...628..973L }}</ref>仙后座PZ也是一顆半規則變星，其變光週期約為925日。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.kusastro.kyoto-u.ac.jp/vsnet/gcvs2/CASPZ.html |title=Variable star PZ CASSIOPEIAE (PZ-CAS) - corlan.net |accessdate=2013-12-15 |archive-date=2013-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131215052753/http://www.kusastro.kyoto-u.ac.jp/vsnet/gcvs2/CASPZ.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

儘管這顆恆星非常明亮，但它距離地球約17800光年（5460[[秒差距|秒差距]]），因此在夜空中較為暗淡。這顆恆星的視星等為8.75等，代表人類肉眼無法看到這顆恆星，需要依靠[[望遠鏡|望遠鏡]]才能看到。<ref name="Cornell">[[:arxiv:1308.3580|Distance and Proper Motion Measurement of the Red Supergiant, PZ Cas, in Very Long Baseline Interferometry H2O Maser Astrometry - Cornell University Library]]</ref>

===體積===
仙后座PZ是其中一顆人類已知體積最大的恆星。天文學家估計，其半徑為[[太陽半徑|太陽半徑]]的1,190–1,940倍（5.53到9.02天文單位），即827,645,000至1,349,270,000公里。<ref name="Astrophysical"/>若把仙后座PZ置於[[太陽系|太陽系]]中心，那麼其表面將超過[[木星|木星]]的軌道（5.204267天文單位，778,547,200公里）<ref name=horizons>{{cite web|last = Yeomans|first = Donald K.|date = 2006-07-13|url = http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/horizons.cgi?find_body=1&body_group=mb&sstr=5|title = HORIZONS Web-Interface for Jupiter Barycenter (Major Body=5)|publisher = [[JPL_Horizons_On-Line_Ephemeris_System|JPL Horizons On-Line Ephemeris System]]|accessdate = 2007-08-08|archive-date = 2019-01-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190109070123/https://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/?horizons|dead-url = no}} – Select "Ephemeris Type: Orbital Elements", "Time Span: 2000-01-01 12:00 to 2000-01-02". ("Target Body: Jupiter Barycenter" and "Center: Sun" should be defaulted to.)</ref>，直迫[[土星|土星]]軌道（9.5820172天文單位，1,433,449,370公里）<ref name="horizons2">{{cite web | last=Yeomans | first=Donald K. | date=2006-07-13 | url=http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/horizons.cgi?find_body=1&body_group=mb&sstr=6 | title=HORIZONS Web-Interface for Saturn Barycenter (Major Body=6) | publisher=[[JPL_Horizons_On-Line_Ephemeris_System|JPL Horizons On-Line Ephemeris System]] | accessdate=2007-08-08 | archive-date=2013-05-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130501170543/http://ssd.jpl.nasa.gov/horizons.cgi?find_body=1&body_group=mb&sstr=6 | dead-url=no }} – Select "Ephemeris Type: Orbital Elements", "Time Span: 2000-01-01 12:00 to 2000-01-02". ("Target Body: Saturn Barycenter" and "Center: Sun" should be defaulted to.)</ref>。光繞這顆恆星一周需時4.82至7.85小時，而光環繞太陽赤道一周僅需時14.5秒。<ref name=sse>{{cite web 
